<h1>Esther Abraham</h1>
<h6>10 November 2019</h6>
<p>Esther Abraham, the bright faithful brilliant star of the Abraham Family, was promoted one week ago to Heaven into the tender living arms of Jesus Christ, our Saviour, and is now enfolded in the bosom of our beloved Heavenly Father like a little lamb.  Truly she is the sacrificed lamb of the coming revival in our land.</p>

